The '''Great Door of the Senate''' was the main entrance to the [[Senate Building/Legends|Senate Building]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. The terminus of the [[Avenue of the Core Founders/Legends|Avenue of the Core Founders]], it led into the [[Atrium of the Senate]]. It was made out of [[Durasteel/Legends|durasteel]] and had the [[Galactic Great Seal|Great Seal of the Republic]] and the sigils of the [[Thousand Worlds]] sculpted into it.

